Package: corpling
Type: Package
Title: Simple Tools for Corpus Linguists
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2016-01-01
Authors@R: person("Earl", "Brown", email = "ekbrown77@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides simple tools for corpus linguistics research.
    The concordancer function, concord(), takes as input a regular expression and
    a character vector and returns as output either a vector with the preceding
    and following contexts separated by tabs from the matches or a preview in R,
    provided by View().
